author: craigmcc
msg: Add a default implementation of RealmConnector for use when no
container-provided authentication and access control is desired.
This should really have gone in a subpackage named "default" to be
consistent with the other implementations, but it turns out that
"default" is a reserved word and the compiler barfs over using it

author: craigmcc
msg: Interface that describes the connection between a Context and a security
domain (realm).  There will generally be an implementation of this interface
per security technology that will be utilized.
